NK103(pe)007:1: // tsa r+ya s+ya d+h+aa tu ti sma ////
NK103(pe)007:4: pradz+ny+aaya bimug taa mo sa mi tsipra ta pan nama h+aa pu ru shatsar+yasamyakash+aastran+aa ma /
NK103(pe)007:6: rtogs goms kyi shes rab kyistshogs brgyad skye lugs gsum las rnam pargrol bade /
NK103(pe)007:7: lhun gnas kyi don dang mthun parblo zhugs pa'iskyes bu
NK103(pe)007:8: chen po ngang la gnas pa'ispyod padon phyin ci ma
NK103(pe)007:9: log par yang dag par sgro skur med par bstan
NK103(pe)007:10: pazhes bya ba / rang bzhin stong nyid mtshan nyid
NK103(pe)007:11: kun mkhyen de ye nas kun la lhun gyis grub
NK103(pe)007:12: pa ni 'gro ba'i skyabs kyi mchog tu gyur pas
NK103(pe)007:13: pazhes bya ba / dpal // de'i rol pa'am rnam
NK103(pe)007:14: pa cir yang 'gag pa med par shar bas don
NK103(pe)007:15: bzhi po kun grub par mdzad pa //
NK103(pe)007:16: gnas lugs ji bzhin pa nyid 1lam gyis sgrib byed
NK103(pe)007:17: dang bral bar son te yang dag pa nyid du
NK103(pe)007:18: rdzogs 2pas // bcom ldan de ye nas gnas pa
NK103(pe)007:19: dang mngon du gyur par mnga' 2mdzad pas gzhi 'bras
NK103(pe)007:21: rang la gnas pa'i don ma rtogs pa lhan skyes
NK103(pe)007:22: bdag gzhan gzung 'dzin du brtags pas snod bcud kyi
NK103(pe)007:24: lam chu bo bzhi brgyud pas mjal zhing rtogs pa'i
NK103(pe)007:25: ngang du goms pa'i grogs rtogs pa la bzla nam
NK103(pe)007:26: mkha' rdo rje'i // don goms pa la gnas par
NK103(pe)007:27: bya ba'i phyir rol pa 'gag med kyi spyod pa
NK103(pe)007:28: mkha' rdo rje'i // bstan // gdul bya kun kyang
NK103(pe)007:29: rang rang gi spyod pa dang mthun pas don la
NK103(pe)007:30: drang ba'i phyir thugs rjes gzhan dgrol ba ni 'gro
NK103(pe)007:32: de yi ngo bo nges pa'i tshig /
NK103(pe)007:33: dbye ba gdeng srog mthun pa'i dpe //
NK103(pe)007:34: nyams rim tshad dang yon tan skyon //
NK103(pe)007:35: rang bzhin gzhi dang 'bras bur lus gnas so //
NK103(pe)007:36: sgo gsum rtogs goms kyi gdeng las ma 'das par //
NK103(pe)007:37: rang 1dang gzhan 1dang gnyis ka grol dang chos kyi 111phyir //
NK103(pe)007:38: bzhi po de'i don du 'gyur ba'i sgo gsum gyi bya ba de //
NK103(pe)007:39: ye shes kyi rol par cir yang 'gag pa med par spyod pa'o //
NK103(pe)007:40: rtogs pa don gyi gdeng chen po'i ngang du goms pa gnas te //
NK103(pe)007:41: 'gro 'dul bya dang nam mkha' bya bral gyis don bzhi grub pa'i //
NK103(pe)007:42: sgo gsum rtsol bas ma btsal rol pa mi 'gag par shar nas //
NK103(pe)007:43: cir yang spyod pas spyod pa'i ming gis don nges pa'i tshig dang ldan pa yin //
NK103(pe)007:45: nam mkha' rdo rje'i spyod pa las //
NK103(pe)007:46: rtogs goms kyi gdeng dang ldan pas rang rgyud pa
NK103(pe)007:47: las lhag pa'i spyod pa gdul bya mos pas so
NK103(pe)007:49: rang nyid lta sgom gyi gdeng la gnas pa des //
NK103(pe)007:51: yi ge 'bri mchod spyin pa dang //
NK103(pe)007:52: nyan dang klog dang len pa dang //
NK103(pe)007:53: 'chad dang kha ton byed pa dang //
NK103(pe)007:54: de sems pa dang sgom pa dang //
NK103(pe)007:55: spyod pa de bcu'i bdag nyid ni //
NK103(pe)007:56: bsod nams phung po dpag tu med //
NK103(pe)007:57: ces pas thun mong ma yin pa'i dge ba theg pa chen po'i chos spyod bcu'i rang bzhin 1dang //
NK103(pe)007:58: sgo gsum ngan lus kyi gsum ngag gi bzhi /
NK103(pe)007:59: yid kyi gsum ste bcu las log nas //
NK103(pe)007:60: dbu ma rin po che'i phreng ba las /
NK103(pe)007:61: mi gsod pa dang rku spong dang //
NK103(pe)007:62: gzhan gyi chung ma spong ba dang //
NK103(pe)007:63: log dang phra ma rtsub nyid dang //
NK103(pe)007:64: ma 'brel smra ba yang dag sdom //
NK103(pe)007:65: chags dang gnod sems med pa pa //
NK103(pe)007:66: nyid kyi lta ba yongs spong ba //
NK103(pe)007:67: 'di dag las lam dkar bcu ste //
NK103(pe)007:68: bzlog pa dag ni nag po yin //
NK103(pe)007:69: zhes pas dge bcu'i don la 1gnas 11par bya //
NK103(pe)007:70: lhun gnas kyi don rtogs pa la dge ba blang ba dang mi dge ba dor ba dang bral //
NK103(pe)007:71: blang dor spyod kyang tshul ngan gyi rtsol ba ma
NK103(pe)007:72: yin te tshul bzang po'i rtsol ba yin bas mnyam
NK103(pe)007:74: mnyam pa la gnas pa de yis blang dor de 0yi go skabs 'byed dgos te chos spyod bcu'ang //
NK103(pe)007:75: rol pa 'gag med du gnas par spyad do //
NK103(pe)007:76: spyad kyang mnyam pa'i don la dge ba blang ba
NK103(pe)007:77: dang mi dge ba dor rgyur mnyam nyid de mi
NK103(pe)007:78: gnas so // gal te nag spyod dang mthun pas gdul bya don la bkrir btub pa la //
NK103(pe)007:79: shan pa dang smad 'tshong rgyud bla ma las /
NK103(pe)007:80: gang zhig yang yang sdig grogs bsten pas sangs rgyas ngan sems ldan gyur dang //
NK103(pe)007:81: dgra bcom pha ma gsod ba bya ba min byed mchog tshogs 'byed pa'i mi //
NK103(pe)007:82: de yang chos nyid nges par bsams na myur du de las thar 'gyur gyis //
NK103(pe)007:83: gang zhig yid ni chos la sdang ba de la thar pa ga la yod //
NK103(pe)007:84: ces gsungs pas skye ba gzhan gyi mtshams med par dmyal bar skye ba'i las //
NK103(pe)007:85: rang bzhin dang sdom ldan kho na la lci ba bcas pa'i kha na ma tho ba kun //
NK103(pe)007:86: mthun 'jug gi spyod pa de yis gdul bya de rim gyis drang zhing gzod don la sbyar //
NK103(pe)007:87: 'o na mi sgrib bam zhe na /
NK103(pe)007:88: gzhan don kho na la nges par dgongs la sgrib pa mi gnas so //
NK103(pe)007:89: ldem por dgongs pa bzhi dang dgongs pa bzhi ste brgyad kyis //
NK103(pe)007:90: sgo gsum rdo rje ma bcos pas don la drang ngo //
NK103(pe)007:91: kun rdzob tu snang tshad rol pa cir yang mi 'gag pa la //
NK103(pe)007:92: brten pa'am dgongs nas gang zag dang chos kyi bdag
NK103(pe)007:93: gi phyogs su 'dzin pa dag la de dag yod
NK103(pe)007:94: do zhe na thabs kyis don la drang ba ni
NK103(pe)007:95: gzhug pa ldem por dgongs pa'o //
NK103(pe)007:96: rang bzhin ka1dang rnam kha1pa dang mtshan nyid ga 1gsum 111la //
NK103(pe)007:97: dgongs te spros kabral dang lhun khagyis grub pa dang //
NK103(pe)007:98: rang ga rig pa kho na yin no zhes mtshan
NK103(pe)007:99: nyid ldem por dgongs pa ste don la dbyer med
NK103(pe)007:100: do // sems can gyi spyod pa nyon mongs brgyad khri bzhi stong gi //
NK103(pe)007:101: gnyen por chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong
NK103(pe)007:102: po der bstan pa ni gnyen po ldem por dgos
NK103(pe)007:103: pa'o // mtshams med pa dgongs 'dus so drug pa las /
NK103(pe)007:104: mtshams med pa yi dam tshig ni //
NK103(pe)007:105: dam tshig ting 'dzin shes rab dang //
NK103(pe)007:106: byang chub sems dang snying rje lnga //
NK103(pe)007:107: bar mtshams med par rgyun mi gcad //
NK103(pe)007:108: 'di ni mtshams med dam tshig yin //
NK103(pe)007:111: pa la gnas na byang chub kyi mchog 'thob bo zhes 'byung ba lta bu /
NK103(pe)007:112: byang chub kyi spyod pa dka' ba la dgongs te gsungs pa'o //
NK103(pe)007:115: dang ma las kyi srid pa /
NK103(pe)007:117: rgyal nyer len dang bcas pa'i rnam shes /
NK103(pe)007:118: po gtsang sbra can gnyis mchog 'dzin gnyis /
NK103(pe)007:120: yul 'khor skye mched drug spyod yul dang bcas pa /
NK103(pe)007:122: mi de dag par 'gyur zhes bya //
NK103(pe)007:123: zhes pa de la sogs ming gis don la bsgyur ba ni bsgyur ba ldem por dgongs pa'o //
NK103(pe)007:124: 'di bzhi ches cher dgongs nas tshig thel gyis mi
NK103(pe)007:125: dbab par bsgyur te lde bu byis pa'i bka' skugs
NK103(pe)007:127: dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa rnams dgongs pa
NK103(pe)007:128: chos sku dang tshogs la sogs pa mnyam pa la
NK103(pe)007:129: dgongs nas // 'das pa'i sangs rgyas de nyid da
NK103(pe)007:130: ltar gyi sangs rgyas de yin zhes mnyam par drang
NK103(pe)007:131: ba ni mnyam pa nyid la dgongs pa'o //
NK103(pe)007:132: de bzhin gshegs pa la mos pa dang mtshan thos pa tsam gyis kyang //
NK103(pe)007:133: mthar thug 'bras bu mi bslu ba'i don gyis dus
NK103(pe)007:134: gzhan la dgongs nas sangs rgyas 'thob bo zhes gsungs
NK103(pe)007:135: pa ni dus gzhan la dgongs pa'o //
NK103(pe)007:136: sangs rgyas dpag tu med pa la dam tshig chos
NK103(pe)007:137: thos pa'i snod la gzod bden pa nges par mthong
NK103(pe)007:138: gi gyi na gzhan gyis mi mthong ngo zhes btags
NK103(pe)007:139: pa lta bu ni lam mthar son ba'i 'bras bu'i
NK103(pe)007:140: don la dgongs pa yin te de ni don gzhan
NK103(pe)007:141: la dgongs ba'o // tshul khrims la sogs pa gang
NK103(pe)007:142: ma nus la gzhug pa'i phyir de la gces spras
NK103(pe)007:143: la dgongs ba'o // su smos shig / sbyin pa
NK103(pe)007:144: la sogs pa gang la zhen pa de dgrol bar
NK103(pe)007:145: bya ba'i phyir gang zhen pa'i phyogs la skyon brjod
NK103(pe)007:146: la dgongs ba'o // su smos shig / pa ste // slob dpon dbyig gnyen gyis /
NK103(pe)007:147: sbyin pa shan pa rnams dang ni //
NK103(pe)007:148: smad 'tshong rnams kyang gtong bar byed //
NK103(pe)007:149: gang yang rung bas tshul khrims ni //
NK103(pe)007:150: srung bar nus pa ma yin no //
NK103(pe)007:151: zhes tshul khrims kyi gtam du gsungs pa lta bu ste /
NK103(pe)007:152: de ni gang zag gi bsam pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK103(pe)007:153: 'di bzhi ni dgongs pa tsam gyi 'gro ba drang ba'o //
NK103(pe)007:154: gdul bya dang mthun 'jug gis drang ba'i thabs su bstan pa yin no //
NK103(pe)007:155: bya bral dang gnas phyogs med nam mkha' la /
NK103(pe)007:156: snying po'i ngang las 'gyur med rdo rjer gnas /
NK103(pe)007:157: zhes pas ma bcos pa'i sems nyid la //
NK103(pe)007:158: lhag par rtogs goms kyi gdeng dang ldan pa'i skyes bu yis //
NK103(pe)007:159: snying po rnal mar bdag gnas na //
NK103(pe)007:160: dge dang mi dge'i chos gang la'ang //
NK103(pe)007:161: lhag par ched du bsten par bya ba min te rtsol med lhug par gnas //
NK103(pe)007:162: 'gro 'dul spyad nam mkha' bzhag don la gnas pa thams cad kyang //
NK103(pe)007:163: nam mkha' ma bcos pa lhag cing 'gro 'dul gyis mthun pa 'dren //
NK103(pe)007:164: spyod pa gnyis po de la yangs dog gi bsam rtsis las 'das so //
NK103(pe)007:165: byang sems rtogs pa'i ngang la goms par gnas pa'i skyes bu chen po la //
NK103(pe)007:166: spyod pa thams cad ye shes thugs rjer rol //
NK103(pe)007:167: pa rnam pa sgyu mar lhun grub pas //
NK103(pe)007:168: blang dor gyi bsam pa dang bral ba ni gdeng chen po dang ldan pa'o //
NK103(pe)007:169: thams cad mnyam pa des na mi mthun phyogs bkag
NK103(pe)007:170: cing spangs pa dang mthun phyogs la spyad pa la
NK103(pe)007:171: // sogs pa'i rjes su sems mi 'brang bar //
NK103(pe)007:172: gang ltar gnas pa de ltar du bde ba'i phyir //
NK103(pe)007:173: blang ba dang dor ba'i yid dang bral ba ni srog gi gzungs so //
NK103(pe)007:174: dper na 'gro bas las gang sgrub der brtson 'grus drag po byas pas //
NK103(pe)007:175: gang 'dod pa'i don la myur du gnas te thob pa ltar //
NK103(pe)007:176: don rtogs pas grub pa'i ngang la gnas pa'i skyes chen gyis //
NK103(pe)007:177: snying por gnas shing don bzhi po kun grub //
NK103(pe)007:178: de yang a ti'i dang po mos pas 'jug zhugs nas rtogs goms kyi ngang du gnas //
NK103(pe)007:179: goms pa tshad du phyin nas 'bras bu dngos su rdzogs pa ni //
NK103(pe)007:180: skyes bu chen po rtogs pa nar son pa la chig chod du rdzogs kyang //
NK103(pe)007:181: thog ma med pa'i bag chags goms pa la nyams de rim gyis gnas //
NK103(pe)007:182: snying por gnas pa las ma g.yos par //
NK103(pe)007:183: don bzhi lhun gyis rdzogs pa ste //
NK103(pe)007:184: bag chags kyis ma gos par don bzhi grub pa ni mthar phyin tshad de //
NK103(pe)007:185: mos pa'i nus pa tshad du phyin pa'i skabs kyang spang bya min no //
NK103(pe)007:186: bdag nyid chen po'i don mkhyen te rtogs goms pa'i ngang las ma g.yos pas //
NK103(pe)007:187: gzhan don ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub pa //
NK103(pe)007:188: de byang chub chen po'i don mthar phyin //
NK103(pe)007:189: pa ni spyod pa lhun gyis grub pa de'i phan yon yin no //
NK103(pe)007:190: spyod pa lhun grub de yi don bral rnal 'byor ni //
NK103(pe)007:191: rtogs pa yar bsnyags 'phangs bstod kyang //
NK103(pe)007:192: bus pa mtshan nyid pa'i theg par gnas pa ste //
NK103(pe)007:193: smon lam btab pa dang mos pa tsam gyis lhun grub de'i don grub pa min no //
NK103(pe)007:194: lhun grub spyod pa'i rang bzhin spros bral ni //
NK103(pe)007:195: mtshan nyid rang rig pa'i rol pa 'gag pa med pa 'char ba de //
NK103(pe)007:196: des na thugs rje'i rnam pa sgyu ma las //
NK103(pe)007:197: btsal ba thams cad dang bral te don thams cad grub pa de nyid don rang bzhin yin no //
NK103(pe)007:198: de yang gzhi nyid dbu ma pa'i spros bral stong pa dang //
NK103(pe)007:199: sems tsam pa'i rang rig pa la gzung 'dzin gyi
NK103(pe)007:200: dri ma rnam par dag par 'dod pa de'i mthar
NK103(pe)007:201: ma thug ste // chos nyid kyi rol pa'i yon tan cir yang shar ba'i phyir //
NK103(pe)007:202: nam mkha' rdo rje dang lhag spyod mthun 'jug thabs kyi spyod pa gzhi yin no //
NK103(pe)007:203: gzhi de rtogs pa mthar phyin pa'i rgyal ba la //
NK103(pe)007:204: 'bras bu sku gsum ye nas lhun gyis grub pas //
NK103(pe)007:205: ched du brtsol bas ma btsal bar don kun lhun gyis grub pa ni //
NK103(pe)007:206: klu dga sha ka 'jog po'i spyi bo yi rgyan
NK103(pe)007:207: gyi nor bu la yon tan lhun grub yod pa
NK103(pe)007:208: bzhin no // mdor bsdu na don kun mkha' spyod yul //
NK103(pe)007:209: rdzogs par mkhyen nas lhun gyis grub //
NK103(pe)007:210: yangs dog ma yin cir yang rol //
NK103(pe)007:211: skyes chen mthu ldan khyad par can //
NK103(pe)007:212: go phye ba'i 'khor ma 'ongs skal ldan bu dang gang la 'dems /
NK103(pe)007:213: lhan cig pa'i 'khor snying po grub pa 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la //
NK103(pe)007:214: dga' rab kho bo gang gis ni lhun gnas kyi
NK103(pe)007:215: don la rtogs goms kyis gnas nas gang 'dems na
NK103(pe)007:216: rtsol ba'i spyod pas ma btsal bar don bzhi lhun
NK103(pe)007:217: gyis rdzogs par // grub kyis khyod kyis kyang nam mkha' dang mthun 'jug go //
NK103(pe)007:218: spyod pa rgya mtsho rtsol ba med par ci bdes gdul bya blo rab 'bring gi //
NK103(pe)007:219: don rnams grub par gyis shig ji ltar yang dang yang du 'dems //
NK103(pe)007:220: kha skad tsam du rdzogs pa chen po bla na med par khas 'ches par byed cing //
NK103(pe)007:221: zhe la spros bral stong pa tsam mam rang rig
NK103(pe)007:222: pa la gzung 'dzin rnam par dag pa sems tsam
NK103(pe)007:223: par ltar la // 'gro don byed tshul sngon smon
NK103(pe)007:224: lam btab pa tsam la ltos nas sems can gyi
NK103(pe)007:225: don byed par 'dod pa'i skyes bu dag ni //
NK103(pe)007:226: byis pa mtshan nyid pa'i 'dod pa can yin la /
NK103(pe)007:227: nga'i 'di las lhag pa'i lta ba med ces kha tshal bskyed pas blo bde bar sems pa ni //
NK103(pe)007:228: bram ze smon lam grub pa'am /
NK103(pe)007:229: mkha' lding gi mchod sdong bsgrubs pas rjes su don
NK103(pe)007:230: 'grub pa lta bu'i phyogs mthun gyi dpe 'ga' tsam
NK103(pe)007:231: mthong zhing thos pas yid ches rung bar 'dod pa
NK103(pe)007:232: ni ga la rigs te rigs ba min no //
NK103(pe)007:233: de dag rdzogs chen du mi rung ba de bas
NK103(pe)007:234: chos thams cad lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs
NK103(pe)007:235: pa'i don // la chos thams cad kyi bcud 'dus
NK103(pe)007:236: pas snying po de rtogs pa'i sor gnas na che
NK103(pe)007:237: ba'i yon tan thams cad lhun gyis grub pas //
NK103(pe)007:238: 'di la grub mtha' phyogs re la mkhas pa kun
NK103(pe)007:239: kyang nges don du gnas par bya bar rigs so
NK103(pe)007:240: // spyod pa rtsol ba med pas lhun grub phyin
NK103(pe)007:241: ci ma log pas yang dag pa'i de gsal bar
NK103(pe)007:242: byed pas sgron me lta bu /
NK103(pe)007:243: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rjes mdzad pa /
NK103(pe)007:244: rdzogs so////rgya gar gyi mkhan po sh+r+ai sing+ha pra b+ha ba ta dang /
NK103(pe)007:245: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba dge slong bee ro tsa
NK103(pe)007:246: nas yul d+ha he na'i 'du khang du zhus shing
NK103(pe)007:247: bsgyur te gtan la phab pa'o //
NK103(pe)007:249: mkhas pa'i bstan bcos la brten nas /
